{"tid":290630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論] 綜援+義工 有無得諗？","createTime":"2017-06-20T02:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T08:16:04.000Z","uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb518677bae34de2c2df9ba49e4221d70ddc741","tid":290630,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"有班妹下妹下既呀公呀婆，成日係度執紙皮汽水罐之類，都唔肯去拎綜援。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知連登仔點諗啦，但我覺得呢班應該唔算係廢老。<br />\n<br />\n當然佢地唔想拎既原因五花八門，有啲話無面，有啲話唔想做社會或政府既負擔之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，不如同佢地講，政府比綜援，而佢地可以自願去幫手去做義工，咁樣去說服佢地，而家唔係攤大手板拎綜援。<br />\n<br />\n我知有人又會講法例呀，行政之類。呢啲只係做法要諗好佢，我提出既呢個係一種概念。同埋，自願係重點。<br />\n<br />\n你地覺得行唔行得通？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d246b05f36d95f1d8f66b1340320e78efc179c","tid":290630,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9679fa517193c87b08dd466972fff3daab15e0","tid":290630,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2e6922ae99de600a2ec109ae99ab0a32488587","tid":290630,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:40:40.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef4de91604a01ec0df84daef521b4847de74cc8","tid":290630,"uid":62565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"理論上可行 諗法唔錯<br />\n不過要諗係 大有一班伸手拎錢等死既廢老新香港人在<br />\n你估下聽倒話要做義工先有得拎綜援 果班等死廢佬同新香港人會點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd83fe6fae7b2fade50a8182365bff004515d464","tid":290630,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理論上可行 諗法唔錯<br />\n不過要諗係 大有一班伸手拎錢等死既廢老新香港人在<br />\n你估下聽倒話要做義工先有得拎綜援 果班等死廢佬同新香港人會點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自願喎，主要目的係令啲唔願拎綜援既老人家去拎，好似最近執紙皮單野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}